title.rendered: VIDEO: Prestige Motorcars X Gas Car Club Morning Run

content.rendered:
Last month Prestige Motorcars and Gas Car Club arranged another one of our morning cruises. We gathered at Plaza Senayan – a popular gathering area for car enthusiasts before cruising before heading towards Take A Bite restaurant in Pluit.

At Take A Bite, the members indulged in their breakfast before experiencing Time Machine – an escape room type of game. Please enjoy this video and stay tuned to see where the next Prestige Motorcars X Gas Car Club Run takes us
